  calc deriv (Λ • A) ε
    _ = ∑ μ, ∑ ν, SpaceTime.distDeriv μ (Λ • A) ε ν •
        Lorentz.CoVector.basis μ ⊗ₜ[ℝ] Lorentz.Vector.basis ν := rfl
    _ = ∑ μ, ∑ ν, (∑ κ, ∑ ρ, (Λ.1 ν κ * Λ⁻¹.1 ρ μ) * SpaceTime.distDeriv ρ A (Λ⁻¹ • ε) κ) •
